1
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:08,000
[Lee Dong Won as Seung Jun]

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:09,640
[Seong Tae as Jae Hyeon]

3
00:00:09,640 --> 00:00:11,450
[Shin Myeong Seong as Ho Yeon]

4
00:00:11,450 --> 00:00:13,200
[Kim Gyu Jong as Ju Won]

5
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:43,900
[Happy Merry Ending]

6
00:00:45,650 --> 00:00:49,300
You must be having a hard time. Your face looks rough.

7
00:00:54,510 --> 00:00:57,942
My little Seung Jun, you used to be so nice when you were younger.

8
00:00:57,942 --> 00:01:00,375
If you don't have anything to say, I will leave now.

9
00:01:00,375 --> 00:01:02,484
What's the rush?

10
00:01:04,542 --> 00:01:07,609
I have a proposal for you.

11
00:01:09,667 --> 00:01:12,225
Do you want to come work for my company?

12
00:01:12,225 --> 00:01:13,809
What?

13
00:01:13,809 --> 00:01:17,434
Your composing skills must have improved by now, right?

14
00:01:22,374 --> 00:01:25,375
You know we don't accept just anybody at our company.

15
00:01:25,375 --> 00:01:28,075
I can hire you because I'm the CEO.

16
00:01:31,008 --> 00:01:32,834
I want nothing to do with you.

17
00:01:32,834 --> 00:01:35,159
Think carefully.

18
00:01:39,250 --> 00:01:41,934
No matter how much you agonize over it...

19
00:01:41,934 --> 00:01:45,109
you'll eventually come running to me.

20
00:01:51,910 --> 00:01:54,350
I'll be leaving now, since Chan Wu is waiting.

21
00:02:15,834 --> 00:02:21,500
[Episode 6: Closing In]

22
00:02:23,977 --> 00:02:27,998
Why... Why is he doing this to me?

23
00:02:27,998 --> 00:02:30,684
What have I done so wrong?

24
00:02:30,684 --> 00:02:32,335
Hey, Seung Jun!

25
00:02:32,335 --> 00:02:34,559
You haven't done anything wrong.

26
00:02:34,559 --> 00:02:37,676
He's just crazy. What other reason would he need?

27
00:02:39,992 --> 00:02:41,834
I just...

28
00:02:41,834 --> 00:02:45,566
I'll just stop everything and live a quiet life,

29
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:51,451
so it would be nice if he could just leave me alone.

30
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,350
Aren't you going home?

31
00:03:20,350 --> 00:03:23,600
Oh, I have to finish something. You go ahead.

32
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,605
- Okay, I'll get going.
- I'm going to clock out now.

33
00:03:25,605 --> 00:03:27,347
Bye.

34
00:03:45,575 --> 00:03:49,075
[Song Jae Hyeon: Why aren't you answering my calls? Call me when you read this. I'm worried.]

35
00:04:12,890 --> 00:04:16,490
[010-890-1877]

36
00:04:16,490 --> 00:04:18,960
[Villa de GD]
[GD Convention | GD Party House | GD Wedding Mall]

37
00:04:34,742 --> 00:04:37,259
- Nuna!
- Oh! Jae Hyeon!

38
00:04:37,259 --> 00:04:39,242
Is Seung Jun done?

39
00:04:39,242 --> 00:04:40,700
Didn't he tell you?

40
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:44,292
- He quit last week.
- What?

41
00:04:44,292 --> 00:04:47,742
We barely managed to get a substitute in time.

42
00:04:47,742 --> 00:04:50,040
I thought I knew him, but apparently not.

43
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,767
Did... Did he say anything?

44
00:04:52,767 --> 00:04:55,200
He just told us that he needed time to rest.

45
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,951
He already made up his mind, so I couldn't stop him.

46
00:04:57,951 --> 00:04:59,867
Oh... I see...

47
00:04:59,867 --> 00:05:03,516
Why? Do you have something to tell him?

48
00:05:03,516 --> 00:05:05,153
It's nothing...

49
00:05:17,370 --> 00:05:19,411
Did you stay up all night again?

50
00:05:29,179 --> 00:05:32,269
I bought some porridge, so heat it up and have some.

51
00:05:32,269 --> 00:05:34,077
I will be back soon.

52
00:05:40,269 --> 00:05:42,744
[Kim Chan Wu]

53
00:05:52,544 --> 00:05:54,600
Hi, Chan Wu.

54
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:59,552
Teacher, they're kicking me out of the company.

55
00:06:00,644 --> 00:06:05,810
I worked so hard for the album, and we were supposed to start recording next week.

56
00:06:06,627 --> 00:06:09,285
I don't understand why they're doing this to me.

57
00:06:09,961 --> 00:06:12,149
Please help me.

58
00:06:17,585 --> 00:06:20,444
Think carefully.

59
00:06:20,444 --> 00:06:22,769
No matter how much you agonize over it...

60
00:06:22,769 --> 00:06:25,886
you'll eventually come running to me.

61
00:06:36,019 --> 00:06:38,960
It's about time for him to show up...

62
00:06:40,893 --> 00:06:44,702
[Lee Seung Jun]

63
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,619
I'm on my way now.

64
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:02,210
Well done, Chan Wu.

65
00:07:02,210 --> 00:07:06,259
CEO, does that mean I can debut?

66
00:07:06,259 --> 00:07:09,905
Of course! Chan Wu, you deserve a debut.

67
00:07:09,905 --> 00:07:16,787
Your vocal coach shouldn't quit in the middle just because he's busy, right?

68
00:07:26,130 --> 00:07:27,180
Thank you very much.

69
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:29,419
Thank you.

70
00:07:41,769 --> 00:07:43,952
Did he break up?

71
00:07:46,244 --> 00:07:47,627
You go!

72
00:07:47,627 --> 00:07:50,202
No, you go!

73
00:07:50,202 --> 00:07:53,077
Please, go...

74
00:07:53,986 --> 00:07:57,769
Boss, do you... want me to set up a blind date?

75
00:07:57,769 --> 00:08:00,400
I know someone really nice.

76
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,790
I think this person would be perfect for you.

77
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:04,144
I don't know...

78
00:08:04,144 --> 00:08:05,869
She's really pretty, really!

79
00:08:05,869 --> 00:08:09,077
Hyeong! Do you want to go out for dinner then?

80
00:08:09,077 --> 00:08:10,844
It's on me!

81
00:08:16,496 --> 00:08:17,903
The two of you should go.

82
00:08:17,903 --> 00:08:20,578
Come on, let's go. You know how stingy he usually is─

83
00:08:20,578 --> 00:08:22,762
It's now or never.

84
00:08:44,895 --> 00:08:47,170
It's not easy to work alone.

85
00:08:47,170 --> 00:08:48,628
You made the right choice.

86
00:08:48,628 --> 00:08:50,948
I didn't come here because of that.

87
00:08:50,948 --> 00:08:53,021
I came because of Chan Wu.

88
00:08:53,712 --> 00:08:55,778
Oh, Chan Wu?

89
00:08:55,778 --> 00:08:57,212
What about him?

90
00:08:57,212 --> 00:08:59,520
Chan Wu has potential.

91
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:01,583
I'm here to ask you a favor.

92
00:09:04,129 --> 00:09:07,478
And what makes you think I will grant it?

93
00:09:07,478 --> 00:09:09,687
You sent Chan Wu to me.

94
00:09:09,687 --> 00:09:11,968
Aren't you still interested in me?

95
00:09:11,968 --> 00:09:13,837
Yes...

96
00:09:13,837 --> 00:09:16,828
There was no one quite like you.

97
00:09:16,828 --> 00:09:19,895
Weren't you the happiest when we were together, too?

98
00:09:19,895 --> 00:09:23,135
I don't think anyone would have been as nice to you as I was.

99
00:09:25,194 --> 00:09:26,912
No.

100
00:09:27,853 --> 00:09:30,403
I wasn't happy then.

101
00:09:30,403 --> 00:09:33,870
It all crumbled down at that moment.

102
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:37,135
So much that I wanted to cut you out of my life.

103
00:09:37,135 --> 00:09:39,645
You never liked me.

104
00:09:39,645 --> 00:09:42,945
You just needed someone to toy with.

105
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:47,320
What are you trying to say?

106
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,196
Chan Wu.

107
00:09:49,196 --> 00:09:52,029
He may rely on you now,

108
00:09:52,645 --> 00:09:55,080
but he will realize it soon enough.

109
00:09:55,837 --> 00:09:57,745
Before that happens...

110
00:09:58,478 --> 00:10:01,595
I'm giving you a chance to be the person he thinks you are.

111
00:10:07,832 --> 00:10:10,370
Having no one beside you...

112
00:10:10,370 --> 00:10:12,720
That's a lonely thing, isn't it?

113
00:10:17,895 --> 00:10:20,145
You're all grown up,

114
00:10:20,145 --> 00:10:22,570
talking to your hyeong like this.

115
00:10:22,570 --> 00:10:24,595
Please.

116
00:10:28,153 --> 00:10:30,296
Wait, Seung Jun.

117
00:10:32,245 --> 00:10:34,537
Okay, I understand.

118
00:10:34,537 --> 00:10:38,245
I will do what you say if we get back together.

119
00:10:40,187 --> 00:10:43,512
Seung Jun, I can do better.

120
00:10:44,170 --> 00:10:46,520
Don't lie to me.

121
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:48,499
I won't fall for it again.

122
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:52,970
Hey! Lee Seung Jun! Hey!

123
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,104
I'll see myself out.

124
00:10:58,104 --> 00:11:01,520
- See you tomorrow.
- See you tomorrow.

125
00:11:20,745 --> 00:11:22,495
You don't have to take me home.

126
00:11:22,495 --> 00:11:24,554
Do I make you uncomfortable?

127
00:11:24,554 --> 00:11:28,270
No... Not uncomfortable.

128
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,770
Do I make you uncomfortable?

129
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:31,961
I'll just watch you get on.

130
00:11:31,961 --> 00:11:33,712
It's here...

131
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:37,480
How quick...

132
00:11:38,295 --> 00:11:40,037
Do you want to get the next one?

133
00:11:40,037 --> 00:11:43,237
No, I'll just get going now.

134
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:52,900
♫ And memories of you ♫

135
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:54,430
♫ When I close my eyes ♫

136
00:11:54,430 --> 00:11:56,570
Wait!

137
00:11:56,570 --> 00:12:00,270
♫ When the wind blows ♫

138
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:07,600
♫ It feels as though you are right in front of me ♫

139
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,850
♫ But even if I reach out my hand ♫

140
00:12:09,850 --> 00:12:12,220
Having no one beside you...

141
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:14,647
That's a lonely thing, isn't it?

142
00:12:18,162 --> 00:12:24,312
The words may have been aimed at him, but they also hit me.

143
00:12:45,682 --> 00:12:48,156
What on earth happened?

144
00:13:01,964 --> 00:13:04,933
- Seung Jun!
- Hey, Seung Jun!

145
00:13:08,105 --> 00:13:10,772
- Let's go!
- Let go!

146
00:13:10,772 --> 00:13:12,671
I said let go.

147
00:13:12,671 --> 00:13:15,730
It's my turn now, and I'm not letting you go.

148
00:13:15,730 --> 00:13:17,188
Seung Jun!

149
00:13:17,188 --> 00:13:18,273
Stop this.

150
00:13:18,273 --> 00:13:19,579
If you don't come with me,

151
00:13:19,579 --> 00:13:21,999
he's not going to come out of this in one piece.

152
00:13:25,022 --> 00:13:26,564
He said no.

153
00:13:26,564 --> 00:13:28,547
Who do you think you're putting your hands on?

154
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:32,122
- Son of a...
- Stop it.

155
00:13:35,838 --> 00:13:38,339
I don't know what it was like before,

156
00:13:38,339 --> 00:13:40,522
but now I'm not letting him go.

157
00:13:40,522 --> 00:13:43,838
Don't ever come near Seung Jun again, or...

158
00:13:45,606 --> 00:13:47,914
I'll make you regret it.

159
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:51,420
♫ When I close my eyes ♫

160
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:55,190
♫ When I sing a song ♫

161
00:13:55,190 --> 00:14:02,470
♫ It feels as though you are right in front of me ♫

162
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:09,870
♫ But even if I reach out my hand, I can't touch you ♫

163
00:14:11,830 --> 00:14:16,970
♫ I hope we can meet again ♫

164
00:14:16,970 --> 00:14:21,810
♫ Outside of what exists in my memories ♫
